"*Snort, Why does he always boss us around" Headstrong says furiously.
Tantrum takes to the air, "Who cares, its time to move" he snarls back.
Headstrong follows him, taking to the air, then when they arrive where
Razorclaw landed, they both hit the ground, and twist around, transforming
into their animal modes. They both immidiatly follow Razorclaw, but instead
of dodging the trees, they bust right through every one that gets in their
way, using their large horns as spears and so on.
